{"tid":1860103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支持醫護無限期罷工","createTime":"2020-02-03T13:10:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T14:05:01.000Z","uid":9566,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"749a80f88acec02735ba9d5c88b3eee6b6cdaba5","tid":1860103,"uid":9566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T13:10:02.000Z","msg":"支持支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18abe76e023dc1613416d7641ab9bccaafcd11dc","tid":1860103,"uid":150536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T13:10:34.000Z","msg":"[醫護總動員罷工] 其他工會都要立即進行全員投票, 即時三罷配合!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1860077\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1860077</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n全香港都要支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9621ca4de1f4651b30ff560075a0e81591d1a392","tid":1860103,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T13:44:06.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\ntwitter要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdCL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=0d272912\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task</span></strong></span> 攞任務"},{"pid":"d6742797bed010e2e07b5d962968918a4b484e3a","tid":1860103,"uid":51625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T13:45:31.000Z","msg":"其實宜家香港應該全面封鎖！所有市民唔好出街，除非經過檢驗／疫情降溫先準出街。"},{"pid":"8297bcce91a06ee2be93bbfcfe6c5c4e915743fe","tid":1860103,"uid":241536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:02:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支持就一齊罷佢老母臭化閪啦</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d4961ce5aff120621e08c86d2b4108cbae391746","tid":1860103,"uid":102491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:05:01.000Z","msg":"支持你地<br />\n光復香港 跪啦臭閪柒婆<br />\n#手動轉<br />\n<br />\n香港實在太荒誕。<br />\n<br />\nTrain一個警察，只需要幾個月。<br />\n而考警察只需5科合格，體能又合格就得，<br />\n無太多學歷要求，所以毅進畢業就得。<br />\n<br />\nTrain一位護士，起碼要4年時間，<br />\n要出placement，又要讀好多理論，<br />\nTrain一位化驗師/放射治療/物理治療等醫護專業，<br />\n都要4年以上，又係要好長實習期，理論亦唔容易。<br />\n考入去讀呢啲醫護專業，點止要5科合格呢？<br />\n你DSE冇返幾個5，A-level冇返幾個C都入唔到。<br />\n毅進仔⋯以前HKCEE已經畀人踢走，點升AL？<br />\n<br />\nTrain一位醫生呢？普通科咪5-6年，專科起碼10年。<br />\n讀得醫嘅個個都係尖子，精英中的精英。<br />\n<br />\n結果呢？一句「止暴制亂」，警察坐享無限行政資源，<br />\nOT無限補水，個個都Full gear上陣，<br />\n過多兩個月又有新玩具玩。<br />\n醫護即使緊守崗位，任勞任怨，OT冇補足，<br />\n公立醫院日日都過full capacity，但竟然要cut資源。<br />\n一個口罩，一件PPE，都要珍而重之。<br />\n因為唔止醫護同工要著，病人都要著。<br />\n醫護就算冇N95，冇ASTM-Level 2口罩都要頂硬上。<br />\n<br />\n半年社運，無一警員殉職，連重傷都唔覺得有。<br />\n但一場即將來臨的瘟疫，<br />\n可以一夜奪去數十，甚至數百前線醫護性命。<br />\n<br />\n散仔會會長可以喪鬧比自己高級的官員都冇後果，<br />\n班醫護隨時因工送命，喊罷工，<br />\n即刻畀人道德強姦，要人地緊守崗位。<br />\n<br />\n即使警隊集體辭職，只要大規模招人，<br />\n幾個月又有人賣命。<br />\n但係若果一名資深醫護殉職，<br />\n要幾耐先有同樣人才可以取代？<br />\n即使只係一個普通醫護，<br />\n都要幾年時間先train返個出黎。<br />\n<br />\n試問生活響一個咁畸型嘅社會，邊個會唔反抗？<br />\n<br />\n#政府高官又點會諗呢D<br />\n#政府最緊要維穩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tw6EOJm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTw6EOJm.png&h=e2ebc40b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}